1317.name: Trust in others (Eurostat (2015))
1317.unit: Scale of 0 (You do not trust any other person) to 10  (Most people can be trusted)
1317.description: Variable of a general nature and refers to the respondent's opinion/feeling. Trust in others does not refer to a specific group of people. On the scale of 0 (You do no trust any other person) to 10 (Most people can be trusted).
